# Mongo collection variables in repositories

Inside repositories, avoid calling `db["collection"]` repeatedly at each query site. Prefer binding the collection once to an explicit variable like `<domain>_collection`.

```python
# ❌ BAD
doc = await db["users"].find_one({"email": email})
await db["users"].insert_one(doc)
```

```python
# ✅ GOOD
user_collection = db["users"]
doc = await user_collection.find_one({"email": email})
await user_collection.insert_one(doc)
```
